Ernest J. Zeringue, MD is the owner of the California IVF: Davis Fertility Center, Inc.

 California IVF: Davis Fertility Center is a private practice clinic located in Davis, California. We are here to help people with their desires to build their family through individualized fertility services. We specialize in providing the most advanced level of care while maintaining a very patient friendly atmosphere. We emphasize patient education and pride ourselves on efficiency. We will help you to maximize your chances becoming pregnant while minimizing the stress that often accompanies such hightech treatments. Our state of the art facility leverages the latest advancements to ensure high pregnancy rates. Your pregnancy and satisfaction with our services are our primary goals. Having a baby can be very stressful and getting help should not be. Let us show you how compassion and personal attention can make a difference.
